const teamleden = {
  'kylian-benna': {
    naam: 'Kylian Benna',
    rollen: ['Project Owner Socials', 'Project Owner Design', 'Project Owner Animations', 'Media Maker Photography', 'Media Maker Studio/Podcasts'],
    foto: '/images/team/kylian.webp',
    fotoPositie: 'center 15%',
    bio: 'Kylian started as a media maker, but quickly grew into an essential creative force within the team. From sharp designs and social content to animations and photography... his work is everywhere. With a sharp eye for both form and story, he takes every project to the next level.',
    bioLang: 'When Kylian knocked on the door of the student media team asking if he could still join last-minute, Jelle and Dave saw an asset for the team straight away. Kylian gets energy from building brands and designing every form of physical and digital design work. From website layouts to infographics, as <strong>Project Owner Design</strong> Kylian makes sure the content is right and the look-and-feel comes across optimally. That makes Kylian the obvious person for structurally creating and posting social media content for multiple clients. That\'s how he grew from media maker into <strong>Project Owner Socials</strong>.<br><br>But Kylian isn\'t just for stills. For 2D animations and moving illustrations, he\'ll happily fire up his MacBook too. As <strong>Project Owner Animations</strong>, Kylian brings even the most complex advisory reports to life and takes viewers along through moving image.<br><br>Beyond all this laptop work, Kylian can also be found at events and conferences as <strong>Media Maker Photography</strong>. Whether it\'s a group photo, atmosphere shot or profile picture... Kylian makes sure the image bank looks the part and the online experience does justice to the event.<br><br>Last but not least, Kylian is sometimes on location as <strong>Media Maker Studio/Podcasts</strong>, where he sets up and records podcasts on location. In short: a creative all-rounder who knows how to put his eye for form and colour to work in many different ways!',
    linkedin: 'https://www.linkedin.com/in/kylian-b-a0a05b270/',
    buiten: 'Kylian has valued style and presentation from a young age. From perfectly pressed trousers to stylish quarter zips, Kylian always shows up looking sharp. The combination of this passion and his creative skills quickly led to his own premium clothing line, Benna. Through his self-built brand and website, he sells ties, caps and quarter zips. With a growing range and a strong focus on branding and storybuilding, this is undoubtedly going to become an even bigger brand.<br><br>When Kylian isn\'t hunting for the finest fabrics and perfect fits, he\'ll happily set an early alarm for Formula 1. He also enjoys a nice glass of wine or a fine champagne with friends, hits a strong ball on the golf course, and loves a culinary evening (in a restaurant or at home).',
    fotos: ['/images/team/kylian-1.webp', '/images/team/kylian-2.webp', '/images/team/kylian-3.webp', '/images/team/kylian-4.webp'],
    fotosBuiten: ['/images/team/kylian-buiten-1.webp', '/images/team/kylian-buiten-2.webp', '/images/team/kylian-buiten-3.webp', '/images/team/kylian-buiten-4.webp'],
    decoratie: { kleur: 'var(--navy)', top: '40px', right: '-120px', size: '480px' },
  },
  'floor-van-der-hoeven': {
    naam: 'Floor van der Hoeven',
    rollen: ['Communications Advisor', 'Project Owner Copywriting', 'Office Manager'],
    foto: '/images/team/floor.webp',
    fotoPositie: 'center 10%',
    bio: 'Floor stood out immediately as a missing puzzle piece within Astrolads. With her feel for communication, structure and content, she brings calm and direction to every project. From client contact to copy and from meetings to interviews... Floor makes sure that what the audience gets to see lines up with the substantive wishes and the entertaining expectations.',
    bioLang: 'If Astrolads were a puzzle, Floor would be a piece that had been missing for a long time. With a love for communication, social topics and organisational management, Floor came along just in time to handle the growing number of clients and projects. From her role as <strong>Communications Advisor</strong>, she\'s the face and point of contact for many collaborations on Astrolads\' behalf. From quotes to planning, and from interviews to safeguarding the essential content… Floor makes sure the end product matches the (substantive) wishes of the client!<br><br>Beyond communications work, Floor is also incredibly word-savvy and genuinely enjoys writing concise, substantively strong texts. So in her role as <strong>Project Owner Copywriting</strong>, she often takes on the task of checking subtitles, writing captions and (news) articles, or drafting scripts.<br><br>In her first week it became clear that Floor also values an inspiring and structured working environment. So she quickly embraced the role of <strong>Office Manager</strong>, in which she works with Joey to keep the office looking presentable.',
    linkedin: 'https://www.linkedin.com/in/floor-van-der-hoeven-496991297/',
    buiten: 'When Floor wants to recharge over the weekend, that doesn\'t mean sleeping in for hours, lying on the couch or getting bored at the dining table. Quite the opposite, in fact, she prefers to be surrounded by her friends all day long. From a casual drink with housemates to a festival in Amsterdam… as long as it\'s fun! Floor is a cheerful presence who likes to put everyone at ease and slots effortlessly into any group.<br><br>To stay physically healthy alongside all this mental relaxation, Floor can often be found at the gym. From bicep curl to glute bridge, as long as it leaves her muscles feeling properly worked!',
    fotos: ['/images/team/floor-1.webp', '/images/team/floor-2.webp', '/images/team/floor-3.webp', '/images/team/floor-4.webp', '/images/team/floor-5.webp'],
    fotosBuiten: ['/images/team/floor-buiten-1.webp', '/images/team/floor-buiten-2.webp', '/images/team/floor-buiten-3.webp', '/images/team/floor-buiten-4.webp'],
    decoratie: { kleur: 'var(--orange)', top: '40px', right: '-120px', size: '480px' },
  },
  'luuk-van-ooijen': {
    naam: 'Luuk van Ooijen',
    rollen: ['Team Manager', 'Finance Manager', 'Project Owner Advertising'],
    foto: '/images/team/luuk.webp',
    fotoPositie: 'center center',
    bio: 'Luuk started as an intern, but quickly grew into one of the driving forces behind Astrolads. From campaigns and numbers to team management, Luuk doesn\'t shy away from any challenge. In fact, he actively seeks them out! With a sharp eye for growth and innovation, he keeps pushing the organisation forward. A huge asset to the team — and one who\'s nowhere near finished developing yet!',
    bioLang: 'Luuk started in 2021 as a business administration intern at Astrolads, but quickly discovered that he found practice much more fun (and educational) than theory. With 3 years of knowledge under his belt, he stopped his studies and started as Astrolads\' very first full-timer in the role of <strong>Student Manager</strong>. Together with Jelle and Dave he supervised several groups of student media teams. Including the teams that Joey, Kylian and Bas took part in.<br><br>Driven by his love for statistics, numbers and cash flow, Luuk quickly took on more responsibility and started working as <strong>Project Owner Advertising</strong>. In this role, he sets up complete social media campaigns and provides clients with comprehensive reports and advice based on numbers. Luuk also started working as a finance officer back then, which has since grown into being <strong>Finance Manager</strong>. In this role, Luuk holds final responsibility for the cash flow and financial health of the organisation.<br><br>In 2025, the organisation was crying out for more overview and planning. Luuk picked up that role flawlessly, shaping the position of <strong>Team Manager</strong>. Within this role, Luuk makes sure deadlines are met, workload is fairly distributed and quality is safeguarded.<br><br>So is Luuk finally settled and content within the organisation? Never! He\'s now leading the development of the AI branch. What can Artificial Intelligence mean for our clients and how can we take that off their hands? An indispensable link in this era, which Luuk is fully exploring.',
    linkedin: 'https://www.linkedin.com/in/luuk-van-ooijen-6b11ab20b/',
    buiten: 'Luuk\'s lucky number? 010! As a proud Rotterdammer, Luuk doesn\'t miss a single Feyenoord match and can be found around (or in) the fountain after pretty much every win. Born and raised in Rotterdam, Luuk is always somewhere in the city (except when he\'s working, of course).<br><br>When the workday is over, Luuk likes to throw a few darts with friends, keep an eye on the stock market, or hit the terrace whenever possible. In short: a man who enjoys life, takes his career seriously, and uses the hours that fall outside of work to truly enjoy himself.',
    fotos: ['/images/team/luuk-1.webp', '/images/team/luuk-2.webp', '/images/team/luuk-3.webp', '/images/team/luuk-4.webp'],
    fotosBuiten: ['/images/team/luuk-buiten-1.webp', '/images/team/luuk-buiten-2.webp', '/images/team/luuk-buiten-3.webp', '/images/team/luuk-buiten-4.webp'],
    decoratie: { kleur: 'var(--navy)', top: '40px', right: '-120px', size: '480px' },
