    naam: 'Thijs Riep',
    rollen: ['Finance Officer', 'Media Maker Advertising'],
    foto: '/images/team/thijs.webp',
    fotoPositie: 'center center',
    bio: 'Thijs flipped the script entirely and traded his settled life for a self-built camper and the freedom of being on the road. Yet he stayed connected to Astrolads, just on his own terms. From various places in the world he now supports the team with advertising, finance and a weekly dose of exercise.',
    bioLang: 'Thijs worked for years as a physiotherapist and had been involved with the organisation for a while as Jelle and Dave\'s freelance personal trainer. After a serious accident, however, Thijs realised that deep down he had another big passion he no longer wanted to put off. Together with his wife he bought an old van, transformed it into a road-ready home-made camper, and set off into the world. Without a plan and without a finish line… just enjoying that beautiful floating ball we find ourselves on.<br><br>Together we looked for ways to shape Thijs\' role within Astrolads in a way that fits his new lifestyle. Looking at which work could be done remotely, and his talent for accuracy and structure, Thijs now works as <strong>Media Maker Advertising</strong>, supporting Luuk in setting up and monitoring online campaigns, and as <strong>Finance Officer</strong>, keeping the (VAT) administration in order.<br><br>He also still calls in online every week to keep several colleagues fit and supple during an hour of personal training!',
    linkedin: '',
