    foto: '/images/team/paulina.webp',
    fotoPositie: 'center center',
    bio: 'Paulina brought not just an international perspective to Astrolads, but also bucketloads of energy and responsibility. With her creative approach and sharp sense for communities, she knows how to bring both people and ideas together.',
    bioLang: 'Paulina was the first international member of the Astrolads team and has made herself indispensable in multiple areas in a short time. Within international collaborations, she\'s usually found in the role of <strong>Media Maker Socials</strong> and <strong>Media Maker Copywriting</strong>, where Paulina makes sure the website, social channels and newsletter always look top-notch. With her high sense of responsibility, she never delivers half-work and makes sure every production crosses the finish line (on time).<br><br>Beyond her many talents within the creative realm, Paulina also has a big heart for the young creative generation in the city. So she fits the role of <strong>Project Owner Community</strong> like no other, from this position she organises (Astrolads Community) events at our office, recruits new members through social media, and makes sure the people the community is meant for actually know about it. This calls for a creative, contemporary approach and a love of the unconventional working week, both of which Paulina masters and embraces.<br><br>In short, Paulina is a unique link in the team, puts Astrolads on the international map, and takes the community to a whole new level!',
