  'sude-kirlioglu': {
    naam: 'Sude Kirlioglu',
    rollen: ['Studio/Podcast Intern', 'Socials Intern', 'Video Intern', 'Office Manager'],
    foto: '/images/team/sude.webp',
    fotoPositie: 'center center',
    bio: 'Quick, sharp and committed. Sude walks in every day with a load of energy and makes herself indispensable on every production in no time. With a heart for the production side of the work, a true maker!',
    bioLang: 'During the first meeting with Sude, we were instantly enthusiastic about the energy she brought in. With a wish to learn more about the production side of media work, Sude started as <strong>Studio/Podcast Intern</strong>, <strong>Socials Intern</strong> and <strong>Video Intern</strong>. It only took a few weeks before audio edits and studio shoot days could barely be passed to anyone else, because Sude was eager to take them on and delivered them at an unprecedented pace to the project owners involved. With such a huge dose of energy and sense of responsibility, Sude has become a fixture in the organisation and we genuinely don\'t want to do without her... that says something!<br><br>Beyond all the productive work, Sude is also a proud member of the facility team as <strong>Office Manager</strong>, and no colleague gets away anymore with a left-behind coffee cup or a hard drive that wasn\'t put back in its place. A rare talent within the organisation that is hugely appreciated, because ultimately it\'s what keeps our workspace looking presentable every day!<br><br>From last-minute intern to studio expert… Sude makes sure everything around productions is sorted to a T!',
    linkedin: 'https://www.linkedin.com/in/sude-kirlioglu-5b226a365/',
    buiten: 'Sude\'s heart beats faster, above all, for many a Korean rock band. From a huge collection of albums to stickers and merchandise… Sude is just shy of being on the tour bus with the band, tickets are booked across Europe to see the concerts in multiple countries.<br><br>And when the music\'s off for a moment and it\'s time for another form of relaxation, you\'ll probably find Sude glued to the screen for the umpteenth watch party of Tick Tick Boom or another rock musical. But it\'s not always music, dance, musicals and collecting! Sude can sometimes embrace the calm too, and thoroughly enjoy a beautiful sunset, a nature walk or a hangout with friends!',
    fotos: ['/images/team/sude-1.webp', '/images/team/sude-2.webp', '/images/team/sude-3.webp', '/images/team/sude-4.webp', '/images/team/sude-5.webp'],
    fotosBuiten: ['/images/team/sude-buiten-1.webp', '/images/team/sude-buiten-2.webp', '/images/team/sude-buiten-3.webp', '/images/team/sude-buiten-4.webp', '/images/team/sude-buiten-5.webp', '/images/team/sude-buiten-6.webp', '/images/team/sude-buiten-7.webp'],
    decoratie: { kleur: 'var(--orange)', top: '40px', right: '-120px', size: '480px' },
  },
  'jamie-kuiper': {
    naam: 'Jamie Kuiper',
    rollen: ['Photography Intern', 'Socials Intern', 'Video Intern', 'Studio/Podcast Intern'],
    foto: '/images/team/jamie.webp',
    fotoPositie: 'center center',
    bio: 'Jamie started behind the camera, but quickly discovered he\'s also right at home in front of it. With his enthusiasm and curiosity, he\'s grown into a creative all-rounder within the team.',
    bioLang: 'Jamie joined as part of the student media team. While he started with camera and edit work, he quickly discovered that he got a lot of joy out of doing interviews and presenting on camera. When the internship ended, he felt he wasn\'t done learning at Astrolads yet, so he applied for an internship spot, and so it happened. Jamie joined the Astrolads team as <strong>Video Intern</strong>, <strong>Socials Intern</strong> and <strong>Studio/Podcast Intern</strong>. It quickly turned out that Jamie also really enjoyed taking photos, and so he gradually rolled into the role of <strong>Photography Intern</strong> too.<br><br>He\'s now a worthy addition to the creative team, playing an increasingly large role in conducting street interviews. He approaches every total stranger fearlessly and with the biggest smile, and knows how to ask the right questions. Jamie is an incredibly eager and enthusiastic addition to our team, open to new challenges and ready to show what he can do.',
    linkedin: 'https://www.linkedin.com/in/jamie-kuiper-b6ba64329/',
    buiten: 'Jamie has one big passion alongside his studies and work at Astrolads: sport! Barely a day goes by where Jamie isn\'t busy with kettlebells, push-ups and deadlifts. For him the gym is a huge energy outlet. But of course there are also hours where he\'s sat on the couch with tired muscles and a tub of quark. Then he most enjoys discovering and testing the latest AI tech, experiencing the digital transformation up close.',
    fotos: ['/images/team/jamie-1.webp', '/images/team/jamie-2.webp', '/images/team/jamie-3.webp', '/images/team/jamie-4.webp'],
    fotosBuiten: ['/images/team/jamie-buiten-1.webp', '/images/team/jamie-buiten-2.webp', '/images/team/jamie-buiten-3.webp', '/images/team/jamie-buiten-4.webp'],
    decoratie: { kleur: 'var(--navy)', top: '40px', right: '-120px', size: '480px' },
  },
  'bas-nieuwenhuijs': {
    naam: 'Bas Nieuwenhuijs',
    rollen: ['Student Supervisor', 'Media Maker Video'],
    foto: '/images/team/bas.webp',
    fotoPositie: 'center center',
    bio: 'Bas stood out early with his calm approach and sharp creative eye. While others seek out the chaos, Bas keeps the overview and brings calm to the process. As both a supervisor and a video maker, he knows how to put people at ease and get the most out of a production. A steady presence with dry humour and a relaxed energy.',
    bioLang: 'Bas joined the student media team and quickly stood out within his group. Because where one creative bounces around and always takes centre stage, Bas is someone who enters the creative process calmly and excels from there.<br><br>Because Bas isn\'t easily rattled and has the long-distance breath to guide any process well, he\'s a natural in his role as <strong>Student Supervisor</strong>. After finishing his studies, he went on to a HBO filmmaking programme and started working with us to supervise the new group of students and pass on the skills he had learned. From guidance on shoot days to making sure everyone arrives on time, Bas makes sure every student tries to get the best out of themselves and learns more from practice in 6 months than they would have in 4 years of theory.<br><br>Alongside his work as a supervisor, Bas is also increasingly in front of the camera as <strong>Media Maker Video</strong>. In this role, Bas does street interviews and presents in front of the greenscreen. Without hesitation he approaches people to question them or put a dilemma to them.<br><br>Bas is a stable factor in the team, who at the same time brings humour and a sense of lightness!',
    linkedin: 'https://www.linkedin.com/in/bas-nieuwenhuijs-3b79531b6/',
    buiten: 'Bas has had a passion for filmmaking from a young age. It was the foundation of his study choice, but is also a hobby he happily pursues in his free hours. He\'s also often (though he\'d like to be more often) found in running shoes. In 2026 this hobby was sealed with his first real medal in the 10km of the CPC run in The Hague.<br><br>And when the running and camera batteries are empty, Bas puts his feet up and fires up the PlayStation. Alone or with friends, saving some innocent civilians or blasting zombies never hurts!',
    fotos: ['/images/team/bas-1.webp', '/images/team/bas-2.webp', '/images/team/bas-3.webp'],
    fotosBuiten: ['/images/team/bas-buiten-1.webp', '/images/team/bas-buiten-2.webp', '/images/team/bas-buiten-3.webp', '/images/team/bas-buiten-4.webp', '/images/team/bas-buiten-5.webp'],
    decoratie: { kleur: 'var(--navy)', top: '40px', right: '-120px', size: '480px' },
  },
  'zofia-michalak': {
    naam: 'Zofia Michalak',
    rollen: ['Community Intern'],
    foto: '/images/team/zofia.webp',
    fotoPositie: 'center center',
    bio: 'With her energy, creativity and open attitude, Zofia grew into a key force within the community in no time. From events to socials, she brings people together and makes everyone feel welcome. A true connector with infectious enthusiasm.',
    bioLang: 'After her internship company was dissolved, Zofia knocked on Astrolads\' door in need of an internship spot. That way she could still successfully wrap up her internship period within a few months. With her roots in Poland, she was perfectly placed as an International Student to get to work on the community team. As <strong>Community Intern</strong> she was given the task of supporting the team at events and polishing and managing the Instagram channel. Zofia grabbed this opportunity with both hands. The community\'s social media channel now runs like a well-oiled machine, and barely a single creative in the city is unaware of the Astrolads Community anymore. She constantly seeks renewal and challenge, and keeps pushing herself creatively.<br><br>Zofia is characterised by an inexhaustible enthusiasm that she expresses in an infectious way. You never need to worry about anyone feeling unwelcome or uncomfortable when Zofia is around, because she\'ll pull out all the stops to make sure you feel welcome. From a listening ear to taking things off your plate… Zofia makes sure you\'re in the right place!<br><br>An ultra-optimistic connector, in short!',
    linkedin: 'https://www.linkedin.com/in/zofia-michalak-a85aa22a0/',
    buiten: 'You might wonder why Zofia even pays rent, because she\'s never home! From rollerskating around the area to concerts of her favourite artists, and from creative events to nature walks… Zofia is constantly out and about gathering new experiences and meeting people. Art galleries and museums aren\'t safe either, because Zofia loves stopping by for creative inspiration.<br><br>In short… if you need Zofia, don\'t look for her at home!',
    fotos: ['/images/team/zofia-1.webp', '/images/team/zofia-2.webp', '/images/team/zofia-3.webp'],
    fotosBuiten: ['/images/team/zofia-buiten-1.webp', '/images/team/zofia-buiten-2.webp', '/images/team/zofia-buiten-3.webp', '/images/team/zofia-buiten-4.webp', '/images/team/zofia-buiten-5.webp', '/images/team/zofia-buiten-6.webp', '/images/team/zofia-buiten-7.webp', '/images/team/zofia-buiten-8.webp', '/images/team/zofia-buiten-9.webp'],
    decoratie: { kleur: 'var(--orange)', top: '40px', right: '-120px', size: '480px' },
  },
  'jelle-van-der-zanden': {
    naam: 'Jelle van der Zanden',
    rollen: ['Co-founder', 'Communications Advisor'],
    foto: '/images/team/jelle.webp',
    fotoPositie: 'center 18%',
    bio: 'Jelle, together with Dave, has been the creative engine behind Astrolads for years. With a deep interest in people, stories and a wide range of topics, he loves diving into something completely to really understand it. He then looks for the connection between ideas, people and perspectives, so that knowledge doesn\'t just stick, but actually sets something in motion.',
    duoBlok: {
      titel: 'Entrepreneurial duo Jelle & Dave',
      tekst: 'The names Jelle & Dave are almost always mentioned in the same breath. A friendship that grew from a shared passion for creating together. First through music, video series and organising events. Then by starting and building Astrolads together. A place that aims to make a valuable contribution to social progress and the development of creative talent. An inexhaustible entrepreneurial duo, both in energy and ideas. And… still best friends!',
      fotos: ['/images/team/jelle-dave-1.webp', '/images/team/jelle-dave-2.webp', '/images/team/jelle-dave-3.webp', '/images/team/jelle-dave-4.webp'],
    },
    bioLang: 'Jelle\'s biggest drive is discovering new worlds and bringing others along. A lifelong learner and connector at heart. He loves diving into a wide range of topics, painting an ever more complete picture of reality. Only to then share it as quickly as possible with others! In projects this shows in his big interest for everyone\'s story, knowledge and unique view. Bringing it all together and building bridges where needed is his greatest strength.<br><br>Within Astrolads, Jelle is mainly active for clients as a <strong>Communications Advisor</strong>. From this role he helps organisations with sharp strategies to optimise internal and external communication, and to link them to practical resources that turn knowledge into momentum. Jelle is also closely involved in productions, as interviewer, director, or armed himself with a photo or video camera.<br><br>When it comes to managing Astrolads, Jelle focuses most on R&D. What developments and opportunities are coming our way, and how do we position ourselves optimally? What do we, as an agency, want to mean for clients and for all the creative talent that finds its way to our office through work, school or community?',
    linkedin: 'https://www.linkedin.com/in/jellepaul/',
    buiten: 'Jelle\'s creativity finds expression in his personal life through making and writing music and poetry. When words fall short, he prefers to have a brush in his hand or enjoys the wonders of nature. He also enjoys diving into books and spends a lot of self-study time on philosophy, history and theology. In short, both in work and beyond, Jelle has an endless curiosity and love for creation.',
   fotos: ['/images/team/jelle-1.webp', '/images/team/jelle-2.webp', '/images/team/jelle-3.webp'],
    fotosBuiten: ['/images/team/jelle-buiten-1.webp', '/images/team/jelle-buiten-2.webp', '/images/team/jelle-buiten-3.webp', '/images/team/jelle-buiten-4.webp', '/images/team/jelle-buiten-5.webp'],
    decoratie: { kleur: 'var(--navy)', top: '40px', right: '-120px', size: '480px' },
  },
  'dave-verwey': {
    naam: 'Dave Verwey',
    rollen: ['Co-founder', 'Communications Advisor'],
    foto: '/images/team/dave.webp',
    fotoPositie: 'center 18%',
    bio: 'Dave, together with Jelle, has been the creative engine behind Astrolads for years. With his energy, humour and huge drive, he gets people and projects moving. In a sea of information and complexity, Dave knows how to quickly grasp the core and translate it with lightness to what really matters.',
    duoBlok: {
      titel: 'Entrepreneurial duo Jelle & Dave',
      tekst: 'The names Jelle & Dave are almost always mentioned in the same breath. A friendship that grew from a shared passion for creating together. First through music, video series and organising events. Then by starting and building Astrolads together. A place that aims to make a valuable contribution to social progress and the development of creative talent. An inexhaustible entrepreneurial duo, both in energy and ideas. And… still best friends!',
      fotos: ['/images/team/jelle-dave-1.webp', '/images/team/jelle-dave-2.webp', '/images/team/jelle-dave-3.webp', '/images/team/jelle-dave-4.webp'],
    },
    bioLang: 'Where he was once labelled AD(H)D and someone with an excessive need for stimulation and renewal, Dave now uses those traits as his greatest strength. With endless energy, disarming humour and a strong drive for progress, Dave makes sure every project moves forward and that everyone involved also experiences the appreciation and enjoyment that meaningful work brings. From a service-oriented and pragmatic mindset, Dave gets energy from thinking along with complex issues and taking on the most relieving role within them. By always keeping one foot in the target audience\'s world and one foot in the client\'s bubble, the right knowledge is translated in the most effective way to where it has impact.<br><br>Within Astrolads, Dave is mainly active for clients as a <strong>Communications Advisor</strong>. From this role he helps organisations with sharp strategies to optimise internal and external communication, turn knowledge into momentum, and link this to practical resources. When it comes to managing Astrolads, Dave focuses via HR & Operations on creating an inspiring working atmosphere where self-development is central, both in the physical space and with the people. From development conversations with the team to renovation projects, and from recruitment to quality management… Dave gets energy from creating (and maintaining) a place where everyone feels at home, can excel personally, and where life enjoyment and a sense of value are central. Besides all this, Dave is also a presentation talent. From live stage to videos and podcasts… Dave brings lightness where things get heavy, and makes the practical translation from complexity.',
    linkedin: 'https://www.linkedin.com/in/davenickverwey/',
    buiten: 'Dave is happiest when actively busy, both physically and mentally. Outside Astrolads this mainly takes shape in his comedy duo <strong>Joey & Dave</strong>. Together with his brother he reached the final of Cameretten in 2022, and since then he tours the country with their own full-length theatre programmes.<br><br>And how does someone who prefers to always be busy actually relax? By running 42.2 kilometres for fun! With his third marathon already on the calendar, Dave has discovered in running a passion he draws energy from and can really \'nerd out\' on.<br><br>And when Dave does give himself a moment to sit down, he prefers to do it playing board games or with a book in hand.',
    fotos: ['/images/team/dave-1.webp', '/images/team/dave-2.webp', '/images/team/dave-3.webp', '/images/team/dave-4.webp', '/images/team/dave-5.webp', '/images/team/dave-6.webp'],
    fotosBuiten: ['/images/team/dave-buiten-1.webp', '/images/team/dave-buiten-2.webp', '/images/team/dave-buiten-3.webp', '/images/team/dave-buiten-4.webp'],
    decoratie: { kleur: 'var(--orange)', top: '40px', right: '-120px', size: '480px' },
  },
};

const data = teamleden[slug as keyof typeof teamleden];
if (!data) return Astro.redirect('/en/about');

const volgorde = [
  'luuk-van-ooijen',
  'floor-van-der-hoeven',
  'joey-meeuwenoord',
  'kylian-benna',
  'jelle-van-der-zanden',
  'dave-verwey',
  'philip-tjahjadi',
  'nick-mooijekind',
  'paulina-kacymirow',
  'bas-nieuwenhuijs',
  'doa-karasahin',
  'thijs-riep',
  'sude-kirlioglu',
  'zofia-michalak',
  'jamie-kuiper',
];

const andereTeamleden = volgorde
  .filter(s => s !== slug && teamleden[s as keyof typeof teamleden])
  .map(s => {
    const d = teamleden[s as keyof typeof teamleden];
    return { slug: s, naam: d.naam, foto: d.foto };
  });
---

<LayoutEN
  title={data.naam}
  description={data.naam + ' is ' + data.rollen[0] + ' at Astrolads. ' + data.bio}
>
  <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify({
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "Person",
    "name": data.naam,
    "jobTitle": data.rollen[0],
    "description": data.bio,
    "image": `https://astrolads.com${data.foto}`,
    "url": `https://astrolads.com/en/team/${slug}`,
    "worksFor": {
      "@type": "Organization",
      "name": "Astrolads",
      "@id": "https://astrolads.com/#organization"
    },
    "knowsAbout": data.rollen,
    ...(data.linkedin ? { "sameAs": [data.linkedin] } : {}),
    "mainEntityOfPage": `https://astrolads.com/en/team/${slug}`
  })} />

  <div class="team-detail">
    <div class="deco-cirkel" aria-hidden="true" style={
      'background:' + data.decoratie.kleur + ';' +
      'width:' + data.decoratie.size + ';' +
      'height:' + data.decoratie.size + ';' +
      'top:' + (data.decoratie.top || 'auto') + ';' +
      'right:' + (data.decoratie.right || 'auto') + ';' +
      'bottom:' + (data.decoratie.bottom || 'auto') + ';' +
      'left:' + (data.decoratie.left || 'auto') + ';'
    }></div>
    <div class="section-inner">
      <Breadcrumb 
        lang="en"
        items={[
          { name: 'About', url: '/en/about' },
          { name: data.naam }
        ]} 
      />

      <!-- Header -->
      <div class="team-header">
        <div class="team-header-left">
          <h1>{data.naam}</h1>
          <div class="rollen">
            {data.rollen.map(r => (
              <span class="rol-pill">{r}</span>
            ))}
          </div>
          <p class="team-bio">{data.bio}</p>
          {data.linkedin && (
            <a href={data.linkedin} class="linkedin-btn" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
              <svg width="16" height="16" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M20.447 20.452h-3.554v-5.569c0-1.328-.027-3.037-1.852-3.037-1.853 0-2.136 1.445-2.136 2.939v5.667H9.351V9h3.414v1.561h.046c.477-.9 1.637-1.85 3.37-1.85 3.601 0 4.267 2.37 4.267 5.455v6.286zM5.337 7.433a2.062 2.062 0 01-2.063-2.065 2.064 2.064 0 112.063 2.065zm1.782 13.019H3.555V9h3.564v11.452zM22.225 0H1.771C.792 0 0 .774 0 1.729v20.542C0 23.227.792 24 1.771 24h20.451C23.2 24 24 23.227 24 22.271V1.729C24 .774 23.2 0 22.222 0h.003z"/></svg>
              LinkedIn
            </a>
          )}
        </div>
        <div class="team-header-img">
          <img src={data.foto} alt={data.naam + ' - ' + data.rollen[0] + ' at Astrolads'} width="480" height="560" loading="eager" fetchpriority="high" decoding="sync" style={'object-position:' + (data.fotoPositie || 'center center')} />
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Duo-blok (alleen Jelle & Dave): tekst LINKS, fader RECHTS -->
      {data.duoBlok && (
        <div class="over-sectie duo-blok">
          <div class="over-tekst">
            <h2>{data.duoBlok.titel}</h2>
            <p>{data.duoBlok.tekst}</p>
          </div>
          <div class="over-fader">
            {data.duoBlok.fotos.map((f, i) => (
              <img
                src={f}
                alt={'Jelle and Dave photo ' + (i + 1)}
                width="480" height="560"
                loading="lazy"
                class:list={['fader-slide', { active: i === 0 }]}
              />
            ))}
            <div class="fader-dots">
              {data.duoBlok.fotos.map((_, i) => (
                <button class:list={['fader-dot', { active: i === 0 }]} data-index={i} aria-label={'Photo ' + (i + 1)}></button>
              ))}
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      )}

      <!-- Over sectie -->
      {data.bioLang && (
        <div class="over-sectie">
          {data.fotos.length > 0 && (
            <div class="over-fader">
              {data.fotos.map((f, i) => (
                <img
                  src={f}
                  alt={data.naam + ' photo ' + (i + 1)}
                  width="480" height="560"
                  loading="lazy"
                  class:list={['fader-slide', { active: i === 0 }]}
                  style={data.fotosPosities && data.fotosPosities[i] ? 'object-position:' + data.fotosPosities[i] : ''}
                />
              ))}
              <div class="fader-dots">
                {data.fotos.map((_, i) => (
                  <button class:list={['fader-dot', { active: i === 0 }]} data-index={i} aria-label={'Photo ' + (i + 1)}></button>
                ))}
              </div>
            </div>
          )}
          <div class="over-tekst">
            <h2>About {data.naam.split(' ')[0]}</h2>
            <p set:html={data.bioLang}></p>
          </div>
        </div>
      )}

      <!-- Outside Astrolads -->
      <div class="over-sectie">
        <div class="over-tekst">
          <h2>Outside Astrolads</h2>
          <p set:html={data.buiten}></p>
        </div>
        {data.fotosBuiten.length > 0 && (
          <div class="over-fader">
            {data.fotosBuiten.map((f, i) => (
              <img
                src={f}
                alt={data.naam + ' outside Astrolads ' + (i + 1)}
                width="480" height="560"
                loading="lazy"
                class:list={['fader-slide', { active: i === 0 }]}
              />
            ))}
            <div class="fader-dots">
              {data.fotosBuiten.map((_, i) => (
                <button class:list={['fader-dot', { active: i === 0 }]} data-index={i} aria-label={'Photo ' + (i + 1)}></button>
              ))}
            </div>
          </div>
        )}
      </div>

      <!-- Our team -->
      <div class="ons-team">
        <h2>Our team</h2>
        <div class="team-grid">
          {andereTeamleden.map(lid => (
            <a href={'/en/team/' + lid.slug} class="team-card">
              <img src={lid.foto} alt={lid.naam} width="300" height="300" loading="lazy" />
              <div class="team-card-body">
                <h3>{lid.naam}</h3>
                <span class="btn-text-arrow" style="margin-top:12px">Read more</span>
              </div>
            </a>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</LayoutEN>

<style>
  .team-detail { padding: 64px 0 96px; position: relative; overflow-x: clip; }

  .deco-cirkel {
    position: absolute;
    border-radius: 50%;
    z-index: 0; pointer-events: none;
  }

  .section-inner { position: relative; z-index: 1; }

  .team-header {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 64px; align-items: start; margin-bottom: 96px;
  }
  .team-header h1 { font-size: clamp(32px, 4vw, 52px); font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 20px; }
  .rollen { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 8px; margin-bottom: 24px; }
  .rol-pill {
    font-size: 12px; background: var(--white);
    border-radius: 999px; padding: 5px 14px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,.12); color: var(--text);
  }
  .team-bio { color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 24px; font-size: 16px; }
  .linkedin-btn {
    display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
    background: #0A66C2; color: #fff;
    text-decoration: none; font-size: 13px;
    border-radius: 999px; padding: 8px 18px;
    transition: opacity .2s;
  }
  .linkedin-btn:hover { opacity: .88; }
  .team-header-img img { width: 100%; border-radius: var(--radius); object-fit: cover; }

  .over-sectie {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 80px; align-items: start; margin-bottom: 96px;
  }

  /* Duo-blok: wit blok met afgeronde hoeken */
  .duo-blok {
    background: var(--white);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    padding: 56px;
    gap: 48px;
    align-items: center;
  }
  .duo-blok .over-fader {
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    overflow: hidden;
    aspect-ratio: 4/3;
  }
  .over-tekst h2 { font-size: 32px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 24px; }
  .over-tekst p { color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.8; font-size: 15px; }
  .over-tekst p strong { color: var(--text); font-weight: 700; }

  .over-fader {
    position: relative; border-radius: var(--radius);
    overflow: hidden; aspect-ratio: 4/5;
  }
  .fader-slide {
    position: absolute; inset: 0;
    width: 100%; height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover; opacity: 0;
    transition: opacity .8s ease;
  }
  .fader-slide.active { opacity: 1; }
  .fader-dots {
    position: absolute; bottom: 16px; left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    display: flex; gap: 8px; z-index: 2;
  }
  .fader-dot {
    width: 8px; height: 8px; border-radius: 50%;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,.5);
